{
  "texts": [
    "GAI technologies should be seen as complementary tools, rather than standalone sources of knowledge.",
    "Additionally, professional development for educators is essential to help them effectively integrate GAI tools into their classrooms.",
    "While GAI tools can assist in many ways including complex topics, they should support rather than replace human expertise.",
    "This study explored the role of an LLM (ChatGPT) in chemistry education, in chemistry education, focusing on their performance and their ability to foster critical thinking.",
    "By using adversarial prompts, we identified both the strengths and limitations of these models in handling complex chemistry problems."
  ]
}